results.title: Wish You Were Here
results.description: X-Force invades Castle Doom to dismantle the Good Doctor's time platform.

results.title: The Haunting of Castle Doom
results.description: X-Force battles Nazis in Doom's Castle.

results.title: Lower East Side Story
results.description: Risque betrays Warpath by drugging him.

results.title: Tragic Kingdom
results.description: Warpath makes a deal with his captor, Sledge; Dani Moonstar is an Agent of Shield.

results.title: Dani Moonstar is Back--But Is She Friend Or Foe?!
Girl Talk
results.description: Domino is captured by Operation Zero Tolerance; Warpath travels to another dimension at Sledge's request.

results.title: Roadside Attractions
results.description: Domino is altered and freed by Zero Tolerance; X-Force attempts to rescue their captured teammates; Warpath finds The Vanisher in an alternate dimension.

results.title: Under the Knife
results.description: During a fight with the New Brotherhood, Sauron guts Sam.

results.title: Transitions
results.description: Rictor and Domino leave; X-Force splits with Cable and hits the road.

results.title: Heading Down a Whole New Road
Destination: Unknown
results.description: Begin X-Force road trip; Broken down in Ohio.

results.title: Stop Motion
results.description: Warpath is killed by Martynec; Stryfe was behind the Camp Verde Massacre.

results.title: Afterlife
results.description: X-Force battles Stryfe in the Underworld; Warpath returns to life.

results.title: Convergence
results.description: Cannonball re-joins the team.

results.title: Bittersweet Reunions
results.description: Arcade sets up a fight between Domino and Shatterstar; Cannonball catches Sunspot and Meltdown smooching and leaves.

results.title: City of Lost Children
results.description: X-Force stops in a small town where all the children are mutants.

results.title: Burning Desires
results.description: Reignfire abducts X-Force including Sunspot (Which is ironic, because Reignfire is supposed to BE Sunspot).

results.title: Set My Soul On Fire
results.description: Origin of Reignfire; Reignfire merges with Sunspot.

results.title: Flashed Before My Eyes
results.description: 1st Origin of Cable

results.title: The Fire Within
results.description: X-Force helps Bobby purge himself of Reignfire; Bobby sets the team up in a base in San Francisco.

results.title: Hot Lava
results.description: X-Force vacations in Hawaii where they run into old foes who have stolen a sacred object.

results.title: A New Home! A New Member...An Old Friend In Danger!
The Gryphon Agenda
results.description: Bedlam invades the X-Factor compound and asks for their help in rescuing Domino; The device damping Domino's powers is destroyed; Bedlam Joins.

results.title: Homefront
results.description: Origin of Bedlam; Cannonball tangles with some strange customers while visiting his Mother in Kentucky.

results.title: ...By The Sword
results.description: X-Force is teleported to Kentucky where they help Sam ward off the New Deviants; Cannonball Re-Joins the Team.

results.title: Possession
results.description: Half of X-Force is possessed by a Chaos Queen and the other half has to enlist magical help to free them; Dani manifests new powers gained in the fight with the New Deviants.

results.title: Experimental Living
results.description: X-Force returns to Almost Reno to learn the truth about the City of Lost Children.

results.title: The Future of X-Force is In The Cards
Armageddon Now Part 1: Family Matters
results.description: Bedlam finds his long lost brother only to discover he is the leader of the New Hellions.

results.title: Battle With the New Hellions Round 1
Armageddon Now Part Two: Blood & Betrayal
results.description: Jesse learns that his older brother has captured X-Force to use their power in awakening the incredibly deadly Armageddon Man.

results.title: Witness the Destructive Force of Armageddon Man!
Armageddon Now Part 3: Hellions Triumphant!
results.description: A Paradigm controlled X-Force helps the New Hellions awaken the Armageddon Man.

results.title: Underground and Over the Top
results.description: X-Force takes down the Brotherhood; Cable revealed as a cyborg; Sam comes back to life as a "High-Lord."

results.title: Armageddon Now Part 4: Rude Awakening
results.description: King Bedlam loses control of the Armageddon Man and takes off with the Hellions leaving X-Force to take down their powerful foe; Feral severs Siryn's vocal cords.

results.title: Fallout
results.description: Siryn tries to cope with the loss of her powers; Origin of Siryn; Meltdown breaks up with Sunspot; Bobby is corraled by the INS; Siryn Leaves.

results.title: Domino--Caught In The Clutches Of Halloween Jack
Strange Interlude
results.description: Domino is accosted by Halloween Jack and brought to his Chaos Citadel; Domino beats off his advances and brings Jack into the present.

results.title: At the Mercy of a Dying Sun God!
Temple of the Dying Sun
results.description: A pair of Eternals trick X-Force and try to steal Dani's new powers; Sunspot is deported to Brazil.

results.title: Artifacts and Apocrypha
results.description: X-Force invades Genosha to help Pete Wisdom steal a living brain; Selene has a proposition for Sunspot.

results.title: Magnetic Distraction
results.description: X-Force tries to help Pete Wisdom rescue a sentient satellite part from Genosha, but the team has to go through Magneto to get it.

results.title: Family Secrets
results.description: Cannonball breaks his uncle out of jail to find out why he and his father were burying bodies in a Kentucky cornfield when Sam was a child.

results.title: Cracked Foundation
results.description: X-Force tries to stop the Damocles Foundation from merging the essence of Reignfire with a Celestial Gatherer and thus creating a weapon of untold destructive power.

results.title: Temptation
results.description: Selene convinces Sunspot to join the Hellfire Club by promising to bring his dead love to life; Hela forces Blackheart to release Dani from his clutches.

results.title: Fast Lane Part 2: Feel The Rush
